- Refactored Identity package. Now allows for custom IdentityManager, email tasks, and authenticators.
  Identity agilephp.xml configuration element and attributes are now optional
- Refactored ORMFactory::loadDialect to ORMFactory::load
- Comment fix to Remoting class.
- Began aligning code with PEAR coding standards.
- Created SessionProvider and abstracted persistence operations from the SessionScope component. Now
  custom SessionProvider implementations can be created and configured using agilephp.xml. Identity
  package re-integrated with SessionScope component.
- Bug fix to ApplicationScope::destroy resulted in error if temp file has already been deleted
- Created Mailer component
- Removed FirePHP from build target since its not being used. Updated README and TODO